graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks Component<br/>Workbench & Runtime Images]

    %% External Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|base OS| UBI9[Red Hat UBI9/RHEL9 9.6]
    Notebooks -->|alternative base| C9S[CentOS Stream 9]
    Notebooks -->|runtime| Python[Python 3.11/3.12]
    Notebooks -->|UI framework| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4]
    Notebooks -->|backend| JupyterServer[jupyter-server 2.17]
    Notebooks -->|GPU accel| CUDA[NVIDIA CUDA 12.6/12.8]
    Notebooks -->|GPU accel| ROCm[AMD ROCm 6.2/6.3/6.4]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch latest]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow latest]
    Notebooks -->|R env| RStudio[RStudio Server]
    Notebooks -->|VS Code| CodeServer[code-server]
    Notebooks -->|CLI tool| OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift Client oc]
    Notebooks -->|pkg mgmt| micropipenv[micropipenv 1.9.0]
    Notebooks -->|pkg install| uv[uv 0.9.6]

    %% Data Science Libraries
    Notebooks -.->|optional| pandas[pandas]
    Notebooks -.->|optional| sklearn[scikit-learn]
    Notebooks -.->|optional| matplotlib[matplotlib]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller] -->|deploys| Notebooks
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|lists images| Notebooks
    KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines] -->|executes runtimes| Notebooks
    Elyra[Elyra] -->|executes notebooks| Notebooks
    OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy] -->|authenticates| Notebooks
    CertManager[cert-manager] -->|TLS certs| Notebooks
    ImageStream[OpenShift ImageStream] -->|distributes| Notebooks

    %% Build System
    Konflux[Konflux Build System] -->|builds| Notebooks
    QuayRegistry[quay.io Registry] -->|stores| Notebooks

    %% External Services (accessed by workbenches)
    Notebooks -->|storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    Notebooks -->|version control| Git[Git Repositories]
    Notebooks -->|packages| PyPI[Python Package Index]
    Notebooks -->|cluster API| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]

